  "text": "In this section, we present numerical results to examine the impact of the number of transmit antennas, N , and the SNRs of the main channel and the eavesdropper's channel on the secrecy performance. We also compare the performance of the AN transmission schemes with the following schemes: 1) the transmit BF schemes [CITATION_1] where maximal ratio transmission [CITATION_2] is adopted at Alice and 2) the NAE and AE schemes [CITATION_3] .",
